{"tid":1427214,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你老母割乜鳩野唔割死煽動撚","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:26:28.000Z","uid":49028,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aa4244b5b55bce8291f2ea8132ab51e355868385","tid":1427214,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"一日到黑係撚咁煽動入禁區<br />\n除左係鬼我真係唔明點解<br />\n入機場原意係make noise <br />\n同唔會被武力驅散<br />\n入禁區做咩 送頭比人<br />\n順便比材料正苦定性恐襲？<br />\n大條道理可以用武力驅散其他和理非<br />\n依家開始見到入禁區post<br />\n麻煩見一個block一個<br />\n比我見到前線衝禁區<br />\n我一撚定拖鳩佢番來<br />\nCheck鳩佢手機<br />\n唔開/發現係鬼即刻大大力錫佢春袋！<br />\n<br />\n對唔住我語氣重 <br />\n但我打機發覺依家越來越多前線<br />\n開始失去理智<br />\n比鬼煽動做錯誤既事<br />\n結果日日都比人塔走一堆前線<br />\n求下你地 <br />\n永遠要記得不被捕原則<br />\n<br />\n利申：夢遊online 坦職"},{"pid":"3923d3a320949057ee6884a91b6870a62a423ce4","tid":1427214,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c441e90797d2c5f8b62ef6f7d910d4ce4316ffee","tid":1427214,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5eb60d838976acf7393166557800200974c5426","tid":1427214,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4041c5b61d9a3e297083391e50a16071e2428515","tid":1427214,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c